### Add a new employee
POST http://localhost:5000/api/employees/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John",
  "surname": "Doe",
  "gender": "Male",
  "department": "Engineering",
  "salary": 50000
}

### Get all employees
GET http://localhost:5000/api/employees/view

### Get employees by department (Engineering)
# You'll need to implement a route to get employees by department
# Example: GET http://localhost:5000/api/employees/department/engineering

### Update an existing employee
# Replace {id} with the actual employee ID you want to update
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/employees/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "surname": "Johnson",
  "gender": "Female",
  "department": "Marketing",
  "salary": 75000
}

### Delete an employee
# Replace {id} with the actual employee ID you want to delete
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/employees/{id}
